Format Percentages
--one can easilly format percentages in Power BI by pasting the following string in the Format drop down
+#0%;-#0%
--if using the percentage in a title/subtitle or card, you can use the custom format in a string with the convert function
    MomPrefix
        & CONVERT ( FORMAT ( [% Change Margin $ YoY], "+#.0%;-#.0%" ), STRING )
